videos.headline: Watkins takes off for 44-yard TD
videos.description: Quez Watkins catches a short pass and gets into the end zone for a 44-yard Southern Mississippi touchdown.

videos.headline: Abraham keeps it himself to increase Southern Miss' lead
videos.description: Jack Abraham calls his own number and dives into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Abraham keeps it himself to increase Southern Miss' lead) 2020/1/4

videos.headline: McMillan airs it out to McCleskey for a 52-yard TD
videos.description: Justin McMillan throws deep and connects with Jalen McCleskey, who gets into the end zone for a 52-yard Tulane touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McMillan airs it out to McCleskey for a 52-yard TD) 2020/1/4

videos.headline: Jones' TD catch pads Tulane's lead
videos.description: Justin McMillan throws to a wide-open Amare Jones for a 20-yard touchdown to increase Tulane's lead to 30-13 over Southern Mississippi.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jones' TD catch pads Tulane's lead) 2020/1/4
